"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.3.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.3.2</span> 標題：聖殿：海（Temple: sea, tank）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： יָם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： yam)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:23\">1KI 7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:24\">1KI 7:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:25\">1KI 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:25\">1KI 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:39\">1KI 7:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:44\">1KI 7:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:44\">1KI 7:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:17\">2KI 16:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:13\">2KI 25:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:16\">2KI 25:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:8\">1CH 18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:2\">2CH 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:3\">2CH 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:4\">2CH 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:4\">2CH 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:6\">2CH 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:10\">2CH 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:15\">2CH 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:17\">JER 52:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:20\">JER 52:20</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0026_bronze_sea.jpg\" alt=\"藝術家繪製的銅海\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">藝術家繪製的銅海 (© Deutsche Bibelgesellschaft, Stuttgart by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>「海」是一個非常大的水槽或水池，用銅製成，深2.5米（8英呎），直徑5米（16.5英呎），邊緣周長約15米（49英呎）。海的壁厚近8厘米（約3英吋），淨重約為25—30噸或更重。描述海的兩處經文存在容量差異；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:26\">1KI 7:26</a> 給出的容量是38,000升（10,000加侖），而<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:5\">2CH 4:5</a> 給出的容量是57,000升（15,000加侖）。從文本來看，我們並不清楚海的形狀是像碗（半球形）還是像一個直立的圓柱體。根據<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:24\">1KI 7:24</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:3\">2CH 4:3</a> 的描述，其外緣鑄有兩排銅葫蘆（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 譯作“panels”「鑲板」；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 譯作“plants”「植物」）作為裝飾。海的「腿」是十二隻銅牛，分為四組，每組三隻，頭朝外面，海馱在牛的背上。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:6\">2CH 4:6</a> 說明水是供祭司洗滌之用，但沒有給出細節。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在有些語言中，最好使用描述性短語來翻譯「海」；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:23\">1KI 7:23</a> 可譯為，「稱為海的大圓碗」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直譯）。雖然這個盆在希伯來文中稱為<em>yam</em> （「海」），但沒有理由在譯文中保留這個比喻性的名稱。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
